	LIMIATIONS OF THE SYSTEM

•	The system depends on resume quality; poorly formatted resumes may lead to incorrect extraction. 
•	AI may not fully understand context, soft skills, or practical experience. 
•	Fixed match score threshold may not suit all job roles. 
•	Complex resume formats (tables, images) may not be parsed correctly. 
•	Depends on external services (AI, Google Sheets, webhook), which may affect reliability. 
•	No human validation, so decisions may not always be accurate.




